snippet.title: Wakamarina Valley, New Zealand UE4 Recreation
snippet.description:
steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1291330/Wakamarina_Valley_New_Zealand/
itch: https://cavesrd.itch.io/newzealand
The Remaster is here! Added lots of new visual elements, a new area, new assets, camera mechanics, revamped rainy alternate map, a flyable drone, remastered/reoptimised VR mode, and a whole bunch of new things to do. enjoy!

stay updated - https://instagr.am/cavesrd
